=Description=

"Mil-OSS has been established to connect and empower an active community of civilian and military open source software and hardware developers across the U.S.

This grassroots movement is a collection of the geeky, coffee drinking, sandal wearing patriots that work for the U.S. DoD and believe that we must adopt open technology innovation philosophies to effectively defend this nation."


